He Uncovers the Mass Mind Control | Anarchy Radio | Full Action Thriller

When a charismatic and controversial radio host discovers that a multinational corporation is secretly using his frequency to conduct a mass mind control experiment, he must race against time to expose the truth and stop the company's sinister plan, becoming a target himself.

2024.  Stars: Drew Lopez, Leila Collins, Eva Noir
